21506004@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Officials familiar with the meeting said Mr. Bush cited the policy as an example of the sort of congressional requirements the administration contends contribute to the failure of such covert actions as this month's futile effort to oust Panamanian dictator Manuel Noriega.@@@@1@42@@oe@2-2-2013
