21574032@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Which goes to show that the First Law applies in insurance as in anything else: There is no free lunch, there is only marketing.@@@@1@24@@oe@2-2-2013
21574033@unknown@formal@none@1@S@And the Second Law, unique to insurance?@@@@1@7@@oe@2-2-2013
21574034@unknown@formal@none@1@S@If I die early, I win -- a hollow victory, since I can't enjoy it -- and if I live long, the insurer wins.@@@@1@24@@oe@2-2-2013
21574035@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Always.@@@@1@1@@oe@2-2-2013
